{"tid":1598383,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓痾爛屎 關唔關針事","createTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T16:20:22.000Z","uid":122936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"191d47e6f78d4816b7d01bf4798d9caf6486a4fe","tid":1598383,"uid":122936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:00:53.000Z","msg":"屋企兩隻貓，上星期日(22/9)打三合一針第二針。<br />\n隻女個晚痾左一次爛屎，第二日再痾多一次爛，之後就變翻正常靚屎，隻仔就一直靚屎既。<br />\n點知前日(25/9)兩隻開始痾爛屎，又嘔過一兩次，但冇換過糧、冇餵過其他野食。<br />\n睇埋今晚就帶去睇醫生，但想問下關唔關打針事？<br />\n啲屎好爛但唔係臭，冇蟲。<br />\n唉兩晚冇覺好訓，一聽到挖砂聲就起身睇，好擔心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JiqokuR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiqokuR.jpg&h=b7a56bc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"042c42e777c6bbafd21b158cdfe82c8b0d784001","tid":1598383,"uid":21855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"我果隻都係打第二針痾爛屎同嘔<br />\n打俾診所醫生開左抗生素同益生菌<br />\n話可能打完針抵抗力弱<br />\n食唔好先睇醫生<br />\n之後食左2日已經好番lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6096bc467d6e6e2e8498f53479ba3d4e052f2016","tid":1598383,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"D貓咪緊張同有壓力都個屙爛屎"},{"pid":"ab9cc7bf907a34468357d1fd58a5f1262f95e623","tid":1598383,"uid":321724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"可能傷風菌入腸<br />\n屋企隻肥貓幾個禮拜就屙下爛屎<br />\n屙一兩次就正常番<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWzgF3w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWzgF3w.jpg&h=5e37cfe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223590e7b68fd13004744b496466c9dce83f26bf","tid":1598383,"uid":321724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"最緊要係貓貓精唔精神"},{"pid":"abf9177b929c1ba7a3c2245d2973198067500165","tid":1598383,"uid":122936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042c42e777c6bbafd21b158cdfe82c8b0d7